{% from "components/link.jinja" import link %}
{% from "components/list.jinja" import list_item %}
{% from "components/heading.jinja" import heading %}
{% macro historic_documents_content() %}
  <p>
    This is a historic tribunal. The functions of this tribunal have been transferred to the General Regulatory Chamber of the First-tier Tribunal in 2009. The GRC began transferring records to Find Case Law in 2022. To view an archived version of the decisions of this tribunal from 2000-2024 visit the {{ link(content="UK Government Web Archive", href="https://webarchive.nationalarchives.gov.uk/ukgwa/20241206055345/https://transportappeals.decisions.tribunals.gov.uk/Aspx/Default.aspx", attrs={"target": "_blank"}) }}.
  </p>
{% endmacro %}
{% macro website_link(label=None) %}
  {{ label }}
{% endmacro %}
{% macro court_noun_content() %}
  tribunal
{% endmacro %}
{% macro contents_navigation() %}
  {% call list_item() %}
    {{ link(href="#coverage-on-find-case-law", content="Coverage on Find Case Law") }}
  {% endcall %}
  {% call list_item() %}
    {{ link(href="#recent-judgments", content="Recent judgments") }}
  {% endcall %}
  {% call list_item() %}
    {{ link(href="#search-this-tribunal", content="Search this tribunal") }}
  {% endcall %}
  {% call list_item() %}
    {{ link(href="#questions-about-judgments-from-this-tribunal", content="Questions about judgments from this tribunal") }}
  {% endcall %}
{% endmacro %}
{% macro coverage_content() %}
  {{ heading(content="Coverage on Find Case Law", tag="h2") }}
  {% set court_date_range = param|get_court_date_range %}
  {% set court_documents_count = court|get_court_judgments_count|intcomma %}
  <p>
    <strong>Date range</strong> — {{ court_date_range }}
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>What’s included</strong> — We currently hold {{ court_documents_count }} documents from {{ court_date_range }}.
  </p>
  {{ historic_documents_content() }}
{% endmacro %}
{% macro understanding_content() %}
{% endmacro %}
{% macro description_content(start_year=None) %}
  <p>
    The Transport Tribunal heard appeals from decisions of the Traffic Commissioners and of the Registrar of the Driving Standards Agency (subsequently the Registrar of Approved Driving Instructors). Traffic Commissioners are responsible for the licensing and regulation of those who operate heavy goods vehicles, buses and coaches. The Registrar of Approved Driving Instructors is responsible for maintaining the integrity of the Register of Approved Driving Instructors. In 2009 appeals from the Traffic Commissioners were transferred to the Upper Tribunal Administrative Appeals Chamber and appeals from the Registrar of Approved Driving Instructors were transferred to the General Regulatory Chamber of the First–tier Tribunal.
  </p>
{% endmacro %}
{% macro about_content() %}
{% endmacro %}
